dct_title_s: Map of River Front of American Dredging Co. Fronting on the Delaware River in the Township of West Deptford
dct_description_sm: Map covers area of American Dredging Company from Red Bank to Washington Park along the Delaware River.
Pierhead and Bulkhead line of American Dredging Co. along Delaware River shown. Map includes land of William J. Tompson as well.
